@startuml
title State

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Allow an object to change behavior when its internal state changes; appears to change its class.

**Use when**: Object behavior depends on state and must change at runtime.

**Key participants**: Context, State, ConcreteState.
endlegend

class Context {
  -state : State
  +setState(s: State)
  +request()
}

interface State {
  +handle(context: Context)
}

class ConcreteStateA
class ConcreteStateB

State <|.. ConcreteStateA
State <|.. ConcreteStateB
Context o-- State
@enduml